Package: directCareForecastR
Title: Financial Forecasting for Direct Care Providers
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Anthony W.", "Raborn", , "anthony@raborndecisionsciences.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This is the backend that performs data loading, cleaning, manipulation, and provides
    financial forecasts for direct care practices. These practices do not take insurance and generally
    rely on a membership model for consistent income and occasionally on per-visit payers for additional
    income. This backend can import various bookkeeping files to calculate monthly overhead and uses
    statistical models to project income based on user-provided assumptions.
